Grankhul is dangerous and subtle. He never sleeps and is always alert. He is quick and deadly, and has a nasty temper. He manifests as a tall, lean bugbear with oversized eyes and long, slender fingers. He shares his Realm in the Abyss, - Layer 241, Palpitatia - with Skiggaret. 

